OL,3,CWhen should you eat your Easter egg?
OL,4,CWe asked the Archbishop of Wales
OL,6,F"You should eat them before, during
OL,7,Fand after", he told ITV Wales' Rob
OL,8,FShelley.
OL,10,F"There are lots of things to say about
OL,11,FEaster", said the archbishop.
OL,13,FHe continued, describing the
OL,14,Fimportance of places of worship,
OL,15,F"Perhaps one of the most important is
OL,16,Fthat there are going to be places that
OL,17,Fwill offer a different kind of rest,
OL,18,Fnot just time out from the busyness,
OL,19,Fbut the inner rest."
