OL,3,CWhen should you eat your Easter egg?
OL,4,CWe asked the Archbishop of Wales
OL,6,F"I hope that when people come here as
OL,7,Fwell as getting that quiet and being
OL,8,Finspired by the beauty of the
OL,9,Farchitecture, they take some of it
OL,10,Fwith them.
OL,12,F"I hope some of that joy and that
OL,13,Fsense of there being something bigger
OL,14,Fand better goes with them and just
OL,15,Fdissipate into all of the busyness of
OL,16,Fthe life."
