OL,3,CWhen should you eat your Easter egg?
OL,4,CWe asked the Archbishop of Wales
OL,6,FMost Reverend Andrew John also paid
OL,7,Ftribute to people who "show their
OL,8,Ffaith in a selfless, gentle, sometimes
OL,9,Funseen, unassuming quiet way which
OL,10,Fgoes unrecognised - which makes life a
OL,11,Flittle bit better.
OL,13,F"I just want to say thank you for
OL,14,Fputting faith into practice", he said.
